{
  "texts": [
    "RQ 1: What Existing Solutions Address FATE in the Context of Health Care on SMPs?There are 4 identified solutions to FATE in health care discussions on SMPs.",
    "First, fairness in this domain is tackled through calibrated, statistical, and intersectional approaches.",
    "Calibrated fairness seeks to balance equal opportunities with individual differences, such as language or location.",
    "Statistical fairness uses demographic data to prevent biases.",
    "Intersectional fairness examines various aspects of an individual's identity."
  ]
}